data.description: Move-in ready, wonderful family or entertaining home in a great location, just minutes away from shopping, parks and restaurants. Enjoy over $75,000 in upgrades including a huge screened in back porch, wood flooring, custom built ins, 2 1/2 car garage, even a custom indoor dog kennel! Primary bedroom and bathroom on the main floor with large separate vanities, soaking tub and separate shower.  Perfect kitchen for entertaining with an eat-in kitchen with large kitchen island open to family and dining space. Loads of storage space with 42'' kitchen cabinets and a convenient touch kitchen faucet. Beautiful stone front fireplace in family room with gas logs and custom built-ins on either side. All secondary bedrooms have walk-in closets. Use the front room as a bedroom or an office space. Beautiful landscaping with stone beds and large fenced in backyard with extra storage shed. Complete with water softener and sprinkler system.
